如何使用git

1. 你得有个github账号；建个仓库(repository)

2. 安装 git

3. 把central repository(中心仓库)load到本地(local repository)
* 我在c盘下新建目录: C:\code_dxf\xuefgit
* 打开cmd，cd到该目录
* git clone [仓库链接]
* 进到仓库目录，cd one-by-one

4. 我修改了 Version Control 文件，如何提交修改？
* First you stage your files which is where you tell Git which files have changes that you
want to push to your central repository. 
C:\code_dxf\xuefgit\one-day-one>git add "[abs path]"
* C:\code_dxf\xuefgit\one-day-one>git config --global user.email "movebeyondfear@gmail.com"
C:\code_dxf\xuefgit\one-day-one>git config --global user.name "xuefengCrown"
* C:\code_dxf\xuefgit\one-day-one>git commit -m "my first commit"
* git push origin master
Once you enter your GitHub username and password from the command line, your changes
will be pushed to GitHub.


